Package: libgtksourcecompletion1.0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, libgtksourceview2.0-0 (>=2.0.0) 
Description: Library for adds completion support to GtkSourceView.
 This library contains a generic popup to add completion 
 support to GtkSourceView. It has some default events and
 a document words provider that adds (auto)completion of
 previously written words

